# Styling and UI Guidelines

## Styling Constants

Use the predefined styling constants from `constants/styling/`:

### Color System
```typescript
// Use AppColors from constants/styling/colors
import { AppColors } from '@/constants/styling/colors';

const styles = StyleSheet.create({
  container: {
    backgroundColor: AppColors.WHITE,
    borderColor: AppColors.PRIMARY,
  },
});
```

### Spacing System
```typescript
// Use Spacings from constants/styling/spacings
import { Spacings } from '@/constants/styling/spacings';

const styles = StyleSheet.create({
  container: {
    padding: Spacings.STANDART,
    margin: Spacings.SMALL,
  },
});
```

### Typography
```typescript
// Use FontSizes from constants/styling/fonts
import { FontSizes } from '@/constants/styling/fonts';

const styles = StyleSheet.create({
  title: {
    fontSize: FontSizes.LARGE,
    fontWeight: 'bold',
  },
});
```

